reviewText: These disks skip like crazy!!!!! If you could watch the movies, you would probably enjoy them, but these disks are so poorly cut that watching them is impossible. So, any price is too expensive for coasters like these. So disappointed.
Most of the movies were good.
There was not 1 comedy movie on this disk set all just so so movies domes had scratches was very disappointed
Great value for good Entertainment. I enjoy funny, clean, movies that make you feel good at the end of the show.
